sentences: Kevin Ford (born August 7, 1992), also known by his stage name KEVI / PRINCE$$ ROSIE, is an American DJ, producer and singer.
Kevin Ford was born on August 7, 1992 in the United States.
One year after Trevor Dahl began his career, he and Matthew Russell formed Cheat Codes, an electronic dance music trio.
He is originally from Calabasas, California.
Cheat Codes' 2017 hit "No Promises" features Demi Lovato, and their 2019 hit "Ferrari" features Afrojack.
